<item>
            <title>[SLING-1191] Dynamic class loader providers are not reloaded when bundles are updated/installed etc.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SLING-1191</link>
                <project id="12310710" key="SLING">Sling</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While the dynamic class loader is unregistering itself and reregistering, if a bundle is updated that is used for class loading, the dynamic class loader providers are unaware of this.&lt;br/&gt;
So while the new dynamic class loader is using the new classes, for example the jcr class loader provider still uses the old classes - which ends somewhere in a class cast exception&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
