                            <comment id="12778823" author="cziegeler" created="Tue, 17 Nov 2009 11:13:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added a new method to the dynamic class loader provider. release(ClassLoader)&lt;br/&gt;
This method is invoked whenever the dynamic class loader is destroyed. This allows the provider to react on this situation and free any resources.&lt;br/&gt;
When a new dynamic class loader is created, a new class loader is request from the provider.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
